Hello,

We are thrilled to announce that Google's AI Residency Fellowship Programme
is now accepting applications from Pakistan for the 2026 cohort.

This 12-month fully-funded research residency is designed for recent
graduates who want to become AI researchers.

Programme Highlights:
- Duration: 12 months (July 2026 – June 2027)
- Location: Google Zurich / Remote
- Stipend: USD 4,200/month + research budget
- Mentorship from Google Brain and DeepMind researchers
- Possibility of conversion to full-time research role

Eligibility:
- Bachelor's or Master's degree in CS, Mathematics, Statistics, or related
- Strong programming skills (Python preferred)
- Research interest in machine learning, NLP, or computer vision
- No PhD required — this programme is designed for pre-PhD candidates

Required Documents:
- Resume/CV (max 2 pages)
- Statement of Purpose (500 words)
- Two letters of recommendation
- Transcript (unofficial accepted for shortlisting)

Application Deadline: April 28, 2026

Apply here: https://research.google.com/ai-residency/apply
Programme details: https://research.google.com/ai-residency

Questions? Email: airesidency@google.com

Best regards,
Google AI Research Team
